ading text-center    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>NEW YEAR'S EVE COUNTDOWN<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p><\/h2><div class=\"ffb-id-68h7jufc fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Only on Saturday, 31st December 2023<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Step into the new year's celebration, where our Rooftop on the 26th Floor sets the stage for an unforgettable countdown party. Immerse you in the groovy beats, selections of house wine, beers, and cocktails coupled with canape selections, snacks, and never-ending fun...<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">As we wait for the clock to strike midnight, join us for the ultimate countdown to 2024. Raise your glass for a toast and be enchanted by a stunning fireworks display heralding the arrival of the new year.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">With very limited seats, call us to BOOK NOW &amp; get ready to dance, dine, and dazzle your senses!<\/p>\n<p><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-68h7k46l fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Platinum - VND 19,900,000++<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\u2714 Front stage sofa seating (up to 8 people)<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\u2714 3 bottle of Wines (red\/ white\/ sparkling)<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\u2714 1 bottle of premium spirits<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\u2714 Canapes<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Gold - VND 9,990,000++<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\u2714 Table for 4 persons<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\u2714 2 bottle of Wines (red\/ white\/ sparkling)<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\u2714 1 bottle of spirits<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\u2714 Canapes<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Silver - VND 4,990,000++<\/strong><\/p>\n<p